.DT
forget
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
forget

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
forget - Forget spells and other things.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
forget <spell|location number>
.EI
.SP 5 5
forget location <location number>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command allows you to forget a spell or a location you have
been remembering through the use of the 'remember' command for
spells, or the 'Remember' spell in the case of locations.
.EP

.SH Example
.SP 5 5
> forget location 2
.EI
.SP 5 5
You forget the location you were remembering!
.EI
.SP 5 5
> forget Ethereal Light
.EI
.SP 5 5
You forget Ethereal Light.
.EI
